longBusinessSummary: Oriola Oyj provides healthcare and wellbeing products in Sweden and Finland. It also offers vitamins, food and food supplements, sports nutrients, wound care, beauty, and makeup related products. The company offers distribution, licensed medicines, and dose dispensing services, as well as involved in research for pharmacies related products. The company serves pharmacies, healthcare, veterinarians, ecommerce, retail, and digital service sectors. Oriola Oyj is headquartered in Espoo, Finland.
